  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nOn recompiling a project, Truffle doesn't delete old artifacts that no longer correspond to any contract.  This can cause problems with functionality that ingests all the artifacts from a project, since it will take in artifacts that correspond to contracts that no longer exist.  E.g., if a contract is moved from `contracts` to `test`, this can cause problems.",
